Package gw.datatype

Enum Class GWJdbcType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GWJdbcType>
gw.datatype.GWJdbcType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GWJdbcType>, Constable
public enum GWJdbcType extends Enum<GWJdbcType>
Represents JDBC types supported by Guidewire.

Each type is represented in Java according to the following table:

Guidewire JDBC typeEquivalent Java Class
BITBoolean
BLOBBlob
BOOLEANBoolean
CLOBString
DECIMALBigDecimal
DOUBLEDouble
FLOATFloat
INTEGERInteger
TIMESTAMPTimestamp
VARBINARYbyte[]
VARCHARString
SPATIAL_POINTSpatialPoint
SPATIAL_POLYGONSpatialPolygon

For the most part, this table reflects the standard JDBC type -> class mappings, with the following exceptions:

  • BLOB is represented asBlob instead Blob.
  • CLOB is represented as String instead Clob.
  • SPATIAL_POINT and SPATIAL_POLYGON are represented as JDBCType.OTHER.
